#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.221"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.221:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.221:0.2"
msgid "23. Dīghacārikavagga"
msgstr "23. Long Wandering"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.221:0.3"
msgid "221. Paṭhamadīghacārikasutta"
msgstr "221. Long Wandering (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.221:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā dīghacārikaṃ anavatthacārikaṃ anuyuttassa "
"viharato."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks for someone who likes long and "
"aimless wandering."

msgctxt "an5.221:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

#. VAR: gāḷhaṃ → bāḷhaṃ (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.221:1.3"
msgid ""
"Assutaṃ na suṇāti, sutaṃ na pariyodāpeti, sutenekaccena avisārado hoti, "
"gāḷhaṃ rogātaṅkaṃ phusati, na ca mittavā hoti."
msgstr ""
"You don’t learn new things. You don’t clarify what you’ve learned. You lack "
"confidence in some things you have learned. You contract a severe illness. "
"You don’t have any friends."

msgctxt "an5.221:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā dīghacārikaṃ anavatthacārikaṃ anuyuttassa "
"viharato."
msgstr ""
"These are the five drawbacks for someone who likes long and aimless "
"wandering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.221:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā samavatthacāre."
msgstr "There are these five benefits of a reasonable amount of wandering."

msgctxt "an5.221:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.221:2.3"
msgid ""
"Assutaṃ suṇāti, sutaṃ pariyodāpeti, sutenekaccena visārado hoti, na gāḷhaṃ "
"rogātaṅkaṃ phusati, mittavā ca hoti."
msgstr ""
"You learn new things. You clarify what you’ve learned. You have confidence "
"in some things you have learned. You don’t contract severe illness. You have "
"friends."

msgctxt "an5.221:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā samavatthacāre”ti."
msgstr "These are the five benefits of a reasonable amount of wandering.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.221:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
